  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcb\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A boy suffering from blood cancer died tragically after drinking Nadi medicine",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A boy suffering from blood cancer has tragically died due to treatment under the guise of pulse therapy.",
        "According to investigations, the boy's family from Vavunia relied on the person in Urumbrai for treatment and stayed at Vatukottai and got treatment for their son.",
        "A 15-year-old boy from Vavuniya died in a house in Vattukkottai yesterday.",
        "Subsequently, Vattukkottai Police, who conducted investigations into the incident, handed over the dead body to the Jaffna Teaching Hospital.",
        "Subsequently, an autopsy conducted on the body revealed that the boy had leukemia.",
        "In this case, the sudden death inquiry was informed by the parents that the boy was treated at Urumbarai.",
        "This tragic situation has occurred when the boy's parents believed that pulse treatment is better than there is special medicine for blood cancer.",
        "The report of the Sudden Death Investigation Officer and the Forensic Medical Officer will be presented in the Mallagam Magistrate's Court."
      ],
